"Always allow a protocol (tcp/udp) with certain ports or port ranges in WAN-"
"Input and WAN-Forward chain."
msgstr ""
"ອະນຸຍາດໂປຣໂຕຄອນ (tcp/udp) ທີ່ມີພອດ ຫຼື ຊ່ວງພອດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນ Chain WAN-Input ແລະ WAN-"
"Forward ສະເໝີ."

